            <title>[LU-15147] Add option to dump all brw pages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15147</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We currently have the option to dump bulk page contents to the debug log on checksum failures.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s very rarely useful to have the option to dump the contents of all bulk pages to the debug log - regardless of checksum state.&#160; This generates a remarkable amount of log traffic and shouldn&apos;t be enabled often.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
